data.description: Just WOW! It feels like HGTV in here... this meticulously designed home has so many custom features. This 3 bedroom 2 1/2 bathroom home sits conveniently in the coveted Bridgeport school district. It has a magnificent chefs kitchen with quartz countertops and a 95 inch quartz island. This custom designed kitchen also has 5 inch plank Bruce hardwood flooring, custom metal work done by Quality Machine, as well as LED lighting, under cabinet lighting, and designer lighting fixtures. There is also a coffee bar complete with a quartz countertop and storage for all of your accessories. A large gathering room with hardwood flooring opens to the kitchen. An expensive entertainment space with hardwood flooring & exposed brick accents opens up to the bar area. This custom wet bar has tile flooring, exposed brick accents, and granite countertops. There is also a color changing fireplace to keep it nice and cozy. The primary bedroom has new plush carpeting and the bathroom suite features a glass shower with custom tile work. It also has a nook in this primary bedroom that is perfect for babies or books. This home is a must see.
